On 09-Jan-98, C Dimitrakakis wrote:

>Anyway, I will start doing a screen version of wreckage, so that I 
>can use Mungwall and stuff to see what happens..

>Btw, how do you do double-buffering on a screen?
>How do you do double-buffering on a window?

About the same as Blitz-Mode, just set up 2 bitmaps for drawing (before
opening the screen) and then on a screen, use:

ShowBitmap to switch bitmaps.

Always follow this with a VWait before drawing on the other bitmap.

On a window, use BitmapToWindow to switch.



