 Try this:

found = True
shapenum=0
While found
	if (peek.w(addr shape(shapenum))<>0
		shapenum = shapenum+1
	else
		found = False
	end if
wend

Shapes that do not exist have a width of zero, and width is the first 
field in the structure.


