commands that Red When  Excited  forgott to  put in  the
docs for the RI libs.

Well now you proberbly think to your self "So what, they
forgot one or two commands, I have managed without  them
so far!". But it's not only one  or  two  commands, it's
actually as many as *62* commands  that   they   forgot to
shape with the world, and that I so nicly do :-)

This isn't a new discovery by  me, I  have  knows  about
these commands  for  about  5 months  now. I even sent a
complete list of  them to RWD, but I never got any awser
from them, and I  sent them 2 or 3 times to them. I even
sent them to the  list when I found them (back when that
Steve guy from RWD  was active on the list), but I never
got any awnser  from  either Steve, or anyone else, so I
just  put  the  file in  a drawer and forgot about them,
until  a  few  days  ago  when *James L Boyd* e-mailed the
list regarding  3 undocumented commands he had found, so
I though I should send my list one  more  to  the  list,
since people should know of them.

The bold text is  the  librarys name, and  the  librarys
that  has  thier  name  highlighted  (in white text), is
librarys that RWD completly forgot  to even  put in  the
docs. Andthen of course the blue text  is the  commands,
and the black text after them are thier syntaxes.

I hope this helps someone to  find  a  command that they
have been looking  for or  something  like that :-) Well
here's the list then...

 ByE!

 *RIAmosFuncLib*
   #CachesOn# bitmask
   #CachesOff# bitmask
   #GTTagValue# ([tagvalue])
   #EraseAll#
   #SwapBank# (sourcebank,destbank)
   #ChangeDir# dir$
   #SaveExec# filename$,List()

 *RIAppLib*
