 *RIZoneJoyLib*
   #ZoneTableNumber# - retunsthe number of the current Zone table
   #ZoneMode# - returns -1 For 68020 mode OR 0 For 68000 mode
   #ZoneTest#(star_num[,end_num],x,y)


