thinking of adding routines to let it  be  started  from
a CLI (or simular), along with the  file  that should be
loaded (just like Multiview, PPmore, More etc), so  that
you chould use it as a standard view tool for txt files.

Both these program will usethe MUI lib, and they WILL be
FREEWARE.

