You have to set the allowable number of windows to a larger number than
5 in the compiler options. This is what the 'Value out of Maximum Range'
is refering to.

Go to the Compiler Options window from the Compiler Option Menu and in
the bottom left of the window there are some arrows to scroll through
the different fields that have maximum values associated with them. Just
go down to 'windows'
and increase the value.
 
