WBStartup
WBenchToFront_
WbToScreen 0

MaxLen pa$=200
MaxLen fi$=200
Repeat
  snd$=ASLFileRequest$ ("load a sound",pa$,fi$)
  If snd$="" Then End
  Free Sound 0
  LoadSound 0,snd$
  prd=Peek.w(Addr Sound (0)+4)
  lnt=Peek.w(Addr Sound (0)+6)
  NPrint "Period:",prd
  NPrint "Length:",lnt
  Repeat
    Print "Delay :"
    dly.w=Edit(3)
    If dly>0
      Sound 0,15
      VWait dly
      Sound 0,15
    EndIf
  Until dly=0
Forever



